## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not cover all possible applications of sociology in everyday life. Additionally, the information is drawn from publicly available content, which may not reflect the latest academic research or comprehensive sociological theories. Further research and expert consultation could provide a more in-depth understanding of the topic.